WEBVTT

00:01.160 --> 00:02.161
PREVIOUSLY ON "SALEM"...

00:02.200 --> 00:02.791
Anne: FATHER?

00:02.830 --> 00:05.526
[ GASPS ]

00:05.570 --> 00:07.128
Increase:
TAKE HER TO THE CAGE.

00:07.170 --> 00:10.298
Gloriana:
COTTON! COTTON!

00:10.340 --> 00:11.967
Emily: HELLO, FATHER.

00:12.010 --> 00:14.069
Man: YOU'LL BE SOLD STILL,
IF THE WHORES WILL HAVE YOU.

00:16.350 --> 00:17.942
Emily:
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

00:20.220 --> 00:21.869
Cotton: I'M SORRY.

00:21.920 --> 00:24.241
Gloriana: [ CRYING ]

00:24.290 --> 00:27.088
Increase: TAKE HER AS FAR
AS YOUR STEEDS WILL TRAVEL.

00:27.120 --> 00:29.179
Cotton: TELL US, MERCY.
TELL US WHAT YOU SAW.

00:29.230 --> 00:31.551
Mercy:
SHE HELD A SPIDER TO HER NECK.

00:33.100 --> 00:35.250
SHE SEEMED TO FEED IT.

00:35.300 --> 00:36.267
Increase: YOU.

00:36.300 --> 00:37.892
I HEREBY ARREST YOU...

00:37.930 --> 00:39.932
ON THE CHARGE OF WITCHCRAFI'.

00:39.970 --> 00:41.562
GUARDS.

00:53.720 --> 00:55.745
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

00:55.780 --> 00:58.044
[ HORSE WHINNIES ]

01:00.390 --> 01:03.757
[ GASPS ]

01:03.790 --> 01:07.021
[ GROANING ]

01:07.060 --> 01:09.620
YOUR WRATH BURNS LIKE FIRE.

01:09.670 --> 01:12.537
YOU LOOK UPON ME
AS WORTHY OF NOTHING.

01:12.570 --> 01:14.128
YOU ARE OF PURER EYES

01:14.170 --> 01:17.105
THAN TO BEAR TO HAVE ME
IN YOUR SIGHT.

01:19.840 --> 01:21.432
[ GROANS ]

01:21.480 --> 01:24.643
I AM 10,000 TIMES MORE
ABOMINABLE IN YOUR EYES

01:24.680 --> 01:28.241
THAN THE MOST HATEFUL,
VENOMOUS SERPENT IS IN MINE.

01:28.280 --> 01:31.044
[ GROANS ]

01:31.090 --> 01:33.388
MY WICKEDNESS MAKES ME
AS HEAW AS LEAD,

01:33.420 --> 01:35.479
AND IF YOU SHOULD
LET ME GO, LORD,

01:35.520 --> 01:37.784
I WILL PLUNGE
INTO THE BOTI'OMLESS PIT,

01:37.830 --> 01:40.822
AND ALL MY RIGHTEOUSNESS
WOULD HAVE NO MORE INFLUENCE

01:40.860 --> 01:43.067
TO UPHOLD ME
AND KEEP ME OUT OF HELL

01:43.100 --> 01:45.989
THAN A SPIDER'S WEB WOULD HAVE
TO STOP A FALLING ROCK.

01:46.030 --> 01:50.239
[ GROANING ]

01:50.270 --> 01:52.431
[ WHEELS CREAKING ]

02:01.880 --> 02:04.383
Dollie: ANY LAST WORDS
FOR YOUR FATHER?

02:06.520 --> 02:09.853
Emily: MAY THE DEVIL BE AS KIND
AND CONSIDERATE TO YOU

02:09.890 --> 02:12.199
AS YOU WERE TO ME.

02:16.060 --> 02:17.391
[ GRUNTING ]

02:23.470 --> 02:25.438
I MISS MERCY.

02:25.470 --> 02:29.247
Dollie: OUR MERCY
IS ALWAYS WITH US.

02:31.710 --> 02:34.941
PERHAPS THAT'S ONE
OF HER SERVANTS NOW,

02:34.980 --> 02:39.986
WATCHING OVER US AND WEAVING
ITS WEB OF DESTINY.

02:42.660 --> 02:44.719
Mary: MERCY...

02:44.760 --> 02:47.729
MERCY...

02:47.760 --> 02:51.264
YOU CANNOT HIDE FROM ME
IN MY OWN HOUSE.

03:01.910 --> 03:04.504
Mercy: [ SOBBING ]

03:08.120 --> 03:10.748
Mary:
WHY DID YOU DO IT?

03:10.790 --> 03:12.314
HOW COULD YOU?

03:12.360 --> 03:13.759
COME OUT FROM THERE AT ONCE.

03:13.790 --> 03:15.155
Mercy: I DID IT FOR YOU.

03:15.190 --> 03:16.259
Mary: FOR ME?

03:16.290 --> 03:17.882
Mercy:
HE WAS COMING FOR YOU.

03:17.930 --> 03:19.488
IF I HADN'T DONE ANYTHING,

03:19.530 --> 03:21.589
IT WOULD BE YOU
IN THE HOUSE OF PAIN.

03:21.630 --> 03:22.995
YOU SHOULD THANK ME.

03:23.030 --> 03:25.362
Mary: PERHAPS.

03:25.400 --> 03:28.198
BUT IT WAS NOT UP TO YOU.

03:34.240 --> 03:36.208
[ SPIDER CRUNCHES ]

03:39.980 --> 03:42.448
[ "CUPID CARRIES A GUN" PLAYS ]

03:47.620 --> 03:50.350
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

03:50.390 --> 03:51.948
* WITCH DRUMS

03:51.990 --> 03:54.595
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

03:55.830 --> 03:58.424
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

03:58.470 --> 03:59.869
* THE WITCH DRUMS

03:59.900 --> 04:02.437
* BETI'ER PRAY FOR HELL

04:02.470 --> 04:07.772
* NOT HALLELUJAH

04:37.040 --> 04:38.166
[ HORSE WHINNIES ]

04:53.960 --> 04:55.712
[ DOOR HINGES CREAK ]

05:05.870 --> 05:07.895
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

05:15.080 --> 05:18.208
Anne: THERE YOU ARE.

05:46.170 --> 05:49.503
[ BIRD CAWS ]

05:49.550 --> 05:52.519
[ SCREAMING ]

06:00.060 --> 06:03.757
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

06:17.310 --> 06:18.902
[ BREATHES SHAKILY ]

06:21.640 --> 06:24.575
Hale: I HAVE KNOWN TITUBA
EVEN LONGER THAN YOU HAVE,

06:24.610 --> 06:26.578
EVER SINCE
SHE WAS A SMALL CHILD.

06:26.620 --> 06:29.373
WITH ALL THAT SHE HAS ENDURED
IN HER LIFE,

06:29.420 --> 06:32.514
IF THERE IS ANYONE
WHO CAN HOLD OUT, IT IS SHE.

06:32.560 --> 06:34.209
Mary: "IF."

06:34.260 --> 06:35.682
SUCH A SMALL WORD

06:35.720 --> 06:38.951
WITH SUCH IMMENSE CONSEQUENCE
FOR ALL OF US.

06:38.990 --> 06:41.049
Hale:
YOU MUST TRUST HER.

06:41.100 --> 06:43.125
SHE WILL USE THE OPPORTUNITY.

06:43.170 --> 06:46.219
Mary: OPPORTUNITY?

06:46.270 --> 06:49.467
YOU CALL TORTURE AN OPPORTUNITY?

06:49.510 --> 06:52.104
Hale: THE OPPORTUNITY TO DIVERT
INCREASE'S ATTENTION

06:52.140 --> 06:54.631
TO WHERE WE WANT IT
AND AWAY FROM WHERE WE DO NOT.

06:54.680 --> 06:56.409
Mary: I DON'T CARE.

06:56.450 --> 06:57.974
I CAN'T BEAR IT,

06:58.010 --> 07:01.639
THE THOUGHT OF
WHAT HE MIGHT DO TO HER.

07:01.680 --> 07:03.341
I WON'T STAND FOR IT.

07:11.460 --> 07:15.157
Increase:
HA. DO YOU LIKE IT?

07:15.200 --> 07:15.950
"TRUTH TH ROUGH PAIN."

07:16.000 --> 07:17.763
I FIND IT A FITTING,

07:17.800 --> 07:21.896
ALMOST POETIC DEMONSTRATION
TO THE GOOD PEOPLE OF SALEM

07:21.940 --> 07:24.659
AS TO WHAT IS NOW
EXPECTED OF THEM.

07:24.710 --> 07:25.904
HMM?

07:25.940 --> 07:27.601
[ GOAT BLEATS ]

07:27.640 --> 07:33.476
IMAGINE TRANSFORMING THIS HOUSE
OF WOEBEGONE PLEASURE

07:33.520 --> 07:36.011
INTO A PLACE OF REPENTANCE.

07:36.050 --> 07:40.009
I UNDERSTAND ALREADY
THEY CALL IT MY HOUSE OF PAIN.

07:40.060 --> 07:41.482
Mary:
AND YOU APPROVE?

07:41.520 --> 07:44.023
Increase: OH, YES.
YES, INDEED, I DO.

07:44.060 --> 07:46.699
OH, KEEPING THE PAINS OF HELL
FOREMOST IN ONE'S MIND

07:46.730 --> 07:48.698
IS THE SUREST --
NAY, NAY, THE --

07:48.730 --> 07:52.939
THE ONLY ROAD TO PREVENT
SPENDING ETERNITY THERE.

07:52.970 --> 07:55.768
AND HOW MAY I HELP YOU
THIS FINE DAY?

07:55.800 --> 07:59.099
Mary: YOU KEEP SOMEONE HERE
THAT BELONGS TO ME.

07:59.140 --> 08:02.268
Increase: WELL, I HAVE
VERY GOOD REASON TO BELIEVE

08:02.310 --> 08:04.471
THAT SHE BELONGS
TO THE DEVIL HIMSELF.

08:04.510 --> 08:05.875
Mary: NONSENSE.

08:05.910 --> 08:08.117
I'VE KNOWN HER
SINCE WE WERE GIRLS.

08:08.150 --> 08:10.687
TRUTH BE TOLD,
SHE IS NOT JUST MY SERVANT.

08:10.720 --> 08:14.110
SHE IS ALSO MY FRIEND.

08:14.160 --> 08:15.616
Increase:
WELL, I WONDER, THEN,

08:15.660 --> 08:20.120
BECOMING BEFRIENDED
BY -- BY ONE'S MISTRESS

08:20.160 --> 08:22.867
IS PERHAPS THE REASON
THAT SHE WENT ASTRAY.

08:22.900 --> 08:24.162
HMM.

08:24.200 --> 08:25.724
PERHAPS --

08:25.770 --> 08:27.397
PERHAPS IT IS NOT SHE,

08:27.440 --> 08:30.068
BUT -- BUT YOU WHO COULD
MOST BENEFIT FROM BEING HERE.

08:30.110 --> 08:32.465
Cotton: I THINK YOU FORGET TO
WHOM YOU ARE SPEAKING, FATHER.

08:32.510 --> 08:34.375
Increase:
COTTON UP AND ABOUT. GOOD.

08:34.410 --> 08:37.140
NO, NO. I KNOW
THIS IS MARY SIBLEY,

08:37.180 --> 08:38.841
WIFE OF MY FRIEND GEORGE,

08:38.880 --> 08:40.745
UNDER WHOSE UNDER TENDER CARE

08:40.780 --> 08:43.317
HE HAS MYSTERIOUSLY WITHERED
INTO AN INVALID.

08:43.350 --> 08:45.818
Mary: I RESENT YOUR
IMPLICATIONS, SIR.

08:45.850 --> 08:49.217
Increase: I IMPLY NOTHING.
NO, I SAY OUTRIGHT.

08:49.260 --> 08:53.196
AT BEST, I FIND YOU TO BE A WEAK
AND IRRESPONSIBLE WOMAN.

08:53.230 --> 08:59.191
AND AT WORST -- WELL, LET US NOT
EVEN CONSIDER THE WORST.

08:59.230 --> 09:02.939
NO, NO. I SHALL TAKE
RESPONSIBILITY FOR GEORGE

09:02.970 --> 09:06.531
AND FOR THE SLAVE, TITUBA,
FOR THE TIME BEING.

09:06.580 --> 09:09.504
MEANTIME, I SUGGEST
YOU GET YOU HOME

09:09.540 --> 09:12.612
TO MR. SIBLEY'S
HOUSE OF SEVEN GABLES.

09:12.650 --> 09:15.619
COTTON, TO BUSINESS.

09:18.990 --> 09:20.412
[ SIZZLING ]

09:38.910 --> 09:40.400
AH.

09:43.510 --> 09:46.240
TONGUE TEARER.

09:46.280 --> 09:48.077
THIS IS FOR [SHEARS SNIP]

09:48.120 --> 09:49.917
SNIPPING THE LIES
FROM THE MOUTHS

09:49.950 --> 09:52.089
OF THOSE WE QUESTION.

09:52.120 --> 09:53.109
[ SHEARS THUD LIGHTLY ]

09:53.160 --> 09:55.481
SKULL CRUSHER.

09:59.090 --> 10:00.955
BREAST RIPPER.

10:01.000 --> 10:02.149
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:02.200 --> 10:03.758
BOTH OF THESE ARE,

10:03.800 --> 10:07.429
WELL, QUITE APTLY,
IF SOMEWHAT CRUDELY, NAMED.

10:07.470 --> 10:11.258
Cotton: FATHER, I ONCE PRESSED
AN INNOCENT MAN TO DEATH.

10:11.310 --> 10:13.904
THERE MUST BE A BETTER WAY.

10:13.940 --> 10:16.977
FATHER, YOU MUST KNOW,
A TORTURED PRISONER

10:17.010 --> 10:19.808
WILL CONFESS TO ANYTHING
TO STOP THE PAIN --

10:19.850 --> 10:21.943
ANYTHING -- TRUE OR NOT!

10:21.980 --> 10:26.019
Increase:
YES, THAT IS SURELY SO.

10:26.050 --> 10:30.259
BUT YOU -- YOU GROSSLY MISTAKE
MY FACULTIES

10:30.290 --> 10:33.191
IF YOU THINK ME FOOL ENOUGH
TO ACCEPT AS TRUTH

10:33.230 --> 10:37.189
THE FIRST PAINED POURINGS
THAT INVARIABLY COME

10:37.230 --> 10:39.596
FROM THE TORMENTED LIPS.

10:39.630 --> 10:41.268
Cotton: BUT, SIR,
IT IS A SELF-EVIDENT TRUTH --

10:41.300 --> 10:44.428
Increase: I TAKE NO TRUTH
TO BE SELF-EVIDENT,

10:44.470 --> 10:50.375
SAVE PERHAPS THAT WHATEVER ACTS
OF HORROR TAKE PLACE HERE TODAY

10:50.410 --> 10:54.039
ARE DUE ENTIRELY TO YOUR LAXITY
DURING MY ABSENCE.

10:54.080 --> 10:56.719
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:56.750 --> 10:58.547
DO NOT LET HIM MISLEAD YOU.

10:58.590 --> 11:02.287
AND ABANDON ALL HOPE

11:02.320 --> 11:06.529
OF YOUR DELIVERANCE
BY HIM OR BY ANY OTHER AGENT.

11:06.560 --> 11:08.391
NOW, WHAT YOU MUST DO

11:08.430 --> 11:11.991
IS MEDITATE...

11:12.030 --> 11:15.363
ON THESE INSTRUMENTS
WHICH YOU SEE BEFORE YOU.

11:15.400 --> 11:16.560
YOU MUST SET YOUR MIND

11:16.600 --> 11:19.398
FIRMLY IN PURSUIT OF THE GOALS

11:19.440 --> 11:21.078
WHICH YOU MUST ACHIEVE,

11:21.110 --> 11:24.500
THAT OF YOUR SURVIVAL
AND YOUR SALVATION.

11:32.690 --> 11:35.579
THE HERETIC'S FORK.

11:35.620 --> 11:37.679
YES.

11:37.730 --> 11:42.690
TO KEEP YOU ATTENTIVE AND ALERT
DURING THE PROCESS.

11:42.730 --> 11:44.561
AND THIS --

11:44.600 --> 11:46.989
WELL, THIS YOU SURELY
RECOGNIZE --

11:47.040 --> 11:48.359
THUMBSCREWS.

11:48.400 --> 11:50.402
I BELIEVE THESE
TO BE THE SIMPLEST,

11:50.440 --> 11:52.704
AND YET
THE MOST EFFECTIVE METHOD

11:52.740 --> 11:54.708
OF REVEALING THE TRUTH.

12:03.720 --> 12:06.041
AND SO LET US BEGIN.

12:08.090 --> 12:10.524
Cotton: YOU EMPLOY THE VERY
TOOLS OF OPPRESSION

12:10.560 --> 12:12.050
PERFECTED BY THE INQUISITION...

12:12.090 --> 12:13.591
Tituba: [ SOBBING ]

12:13.630 --> 12:15.188
Cotton: ...TOOLS USED
AGAINST GOOD PURITANS

12:15.230 --> 12:18.563
BY THOSE WHO WOULD
CALL US HERETICS.

12:18.600 --> 12:19.794
[ THUMBSCREWS CREAK ]

12:19.840 --> 12:21.239
Tituba: [ WHIMPERS ]

12:21.270 --> 12:23.909
Increase:
FIRE WITH FIRE, MY BOY.

12:27.780 --> 12:31.147
Tituba: [ SCREAMING ]

12:31.180 --> 12:34.013
[ SHEEP BLEATS ]

12:35.750 --> 12:38.548
Mrs. Hale: WHERE IS SHE?
WHERE IS ANNE?

12:38.590 --> 12:39.909
Hale:
YOUR FOOLISH DAUGHTER

12:39.960 --> 12:42.485
HAS DONE SOMETHING
EXCEEDINGLY DANGEROUS.

12:42.520 --> 12:44.249
SHE PUT MY MASK ON.

12:44.290 --> 12:45.882
Mrs. Hale: WELL, BRING HER HOME
THIS INSTANT.

12:45.930 --> 12:47.659
Hale: I CANNOT.

12:50.670 --> 12:52.194
[OBJECT THUDS]

12:54.700 --> 12:57.828
ONLY ONE TRAVELER MAY USE IT
AT A TIME,

12:57.870 --> 12:59.565
AND AS SHE HAS NO EXPERIENCE,

12:59.610 --> 13:02.135
SHE WILL HAVE NO IDEA HOW TO
USE IT IN ORDER TO GET BACK.

13:02.180 --> 13:05.672
THE ONLY POSSIBLE USE FOR IT NOW
IS AS EVIDENCE AGAINST ME.

13:05.710 --> 13:07.075
Mrs. Hale:
BUT WHERE HAS SHE GONE?

13:07.120 --> 13:09.611
Hale: TO THE WOODS.

13:09.650 --> 13:11.413
I SHALL FIND HER.

13:11.450 --> 13:16.979
Mrs. Hale: YOU, MAN ENOUGH
TO FACE INDIANS...

13:17.030 --> 13:19.089
AND WOLVES

13:19.130 --> 13:20.825
OR THE DEVILS
YOU PRETEND TO COMMAND?

13:20.860 --> 13:22.088
Hale:
THERE IS NO ALTERNATIVE.

13:22.130 --> 13:24.519
Mrs. Hale: FIND ONE,

13:24.570 --> 13:26.834
FOR I SWEAR BY --

13:26.870 --> 13:29.691
BY WHATEVER IT IS YOU HOLD HOLY,

13:29.740 --> 13:33.528
IF OUR DAUGHTER IS NOT ASLEEP
IN HER OWN BED THIS VERY NIGHT,

13:33.580 --> 13:36.708
MY TONGUE WILL WAG
UNTIL YOU ARE TIED TO A STAKE

13:36.740 --> 13:38.276
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE COMMONS.

13:38.310 --> 13:40.119
Hale: TAKE CARE, WIFE.

13:40.150 --> 13:42.516
YOU SHALL ONLY
IMPLICATE YOURSELF.

13:42.550 --> 13:46.543
Mrs. Hale: THEN WE WILL TASTE
EACH OTHER'S ASHES.

13:52.190 --> 13:56.627
Anne: THIS IS A DREAM --
NOTHING BUT A WAKING DREAM.

13:56.660 --> 13:58.992
THE MASK.

13:59.030 --> 14:00.497
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

14:00.540 --> 14:03.304
MY FATHER'S STUDY.

14:03.340 --> 14:05.865
THESE WOODS.

14:05.910 --> 14:08.174
IT'S ALL BUT A DREAM.

14:08.210 --> 14:14.319
AT THIS MOMENT, I LIE [GASPS]
UPON MY BED IN MY ROOM...

14:14.350 --> 14:16.443
AT HOME.

14:18.850 --> 14:21.353
WAKE UP!

14:22.690 --> 14:24.555
WAKE UP!

14:24.590 --> 14:25.921
[ PANTING ]

14:29.030 --> 14:31.919
IT DOESN'T MATTER
HOW I GOT HERE.

14:31.970 --> 14:33.938
I MUST GET BACK TO SALEM.

14:36.270 --> 14:38.033
EAST.

14:40.040 --> 14:41.928
THIS WAY. [ GASPS ]

14:49.620 --> 14:51.884
Alden: WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
SHE'S IN THE WOODS?

14:51.920 --> 14:54.457
Hale:
I-I KNOW MY DAUGHTER,

14:54.490 --> 14:58.278
HOW SHE THINKS
AND HOW AT TIMES SHE DOESN'T.

14:58.330 --> 15:01.959
I-I KNOW YOU FEEL
THAT I HAVE SOMEHOW FAILED

15:02.000 --> 15:03.888
IN MY DUTIES AS -- AS MAGISTRATE

15:03.930 --> 15:06.228
TO UPHOLD THE NATURAL RIGHTS
HERE IN SALEM

15:06.270 --> 15:11.765
AND THAT YOU HOLD WHATEVER DARK
SUSPICIONS YOU DO ABOUT ME.

15:11.810 --> 15:15.132
BUT I ASK NOT FOR MYSELF.

15:17.650 --> 15:19.345
FOR ANNE.

15:25.790 --> 15:27.280
Alden: LET'S GO.

15:27.320 --> 15:29.208
Hale: THANK YOU.

15:29.260 --> 15:32.991
Alden: YOU CAN THANK ME
IF WE FIND HER...ALIVE.

15:35.700 --> 15:38.624
Cotton:
SAVE US FROM HELL, FATHER?!

15:38.670 --> 15:42.231
IS THAT WHAT YOU'RE DOING --
SAVING US FROM HELL?

15:42.270 --> 15:43.965
WELL, TOO LATE.

15:44.010 --> 15:45.307
SALEM IS HELL,
AND I AM NOT OUT OF IT.

15:45.340 --> 15:47.900
I AM THE CREATURE YOU HAVE MADE.

15:47.940 --> 15:49.601
I CANNOT BE
WHO YOU WILL ME TO BE,

15:49.640 --> 15:51.107
YET I LACK THE WILL
TO BE ANYTHING ELSE.

15:51.150 --> 15:52.777
LIKE THAT MONSTROUS BIRTH,

15:52.810 --> 15:55.142
IT WERE BETTER
HAD I NEVER BEEN BORN.

15:55.180 --> 15:57.512
THOUGH I CANNOT DRAW BACK
THE SANDS OF TIME,

15:57.550 --> 16:00.815
I CAN BREAK THE HOURGLASS.

16:04.960 --> 16:07.292
GOODBYE, FATHER.

16:07.330 --> 16:09.321
I WILL MAKE MY HOME IN HELL
AND AWAIT YOU THERE.

16:20.210 --> 16:23.600
[ GASPS ]

16:23.650 --> 16:26.175
[ YELLING ]

16:31.820 --> 16:33.549
WEAK.

16:33.590 --> 16:37.924
TOO WEAK EVEN TO SNUFF
THIS FEEBLE CANDLE.

16:41.530 --> 16:43.794
[ SOBBING ]

16:43.830 --> 16:46.822
Increase:
WELL, YOU'RE WONDERFUL.

16:46.870 --> 16:48.462
QUITE REMARKABLE.

16:48.500 --> 16:51.663
YOU'VE NAMED AT LEAST HALF
THE PEOPLE IN THE VILLAGE.

16:51.710 --> 16:54.873
OF COURSE,
NONE OF THEM ARE WITCHES.

16:54.910 --> 16:59.745
THE FACT THAT YOU OFFER THEM UP
SO EAGERLY ATTESTS TO THAT.

16:59.780 --> 17:02.840
BUT YOU MADE GREAT PROGRESS.

17:02.880 --> 17:07.249
WE ARE WORKING OUR WAY
THROUGH THE LIES.

17:07.290 --> 17:08.757
[ CHAINS JINGLE ]

17:08.790 --> 17:14.649
VERY SOON, WE WILL COME
TO THAT PRECISE MOMENT

17:14.700 --> 17:18.522
WHEN THE AGONY
WILL BE SO UNENDURABLE

17:18.570 --> 17:21.232
THAT EVEN A-A LOYAL SERVANT

17:21.270 --> 17:24.933
OF THE PRINCE OF LIES
CAN LIE NO LONGER.

17:26.740 --> 17:28.105
AH.

17:35.720 --> 17:38.746
THIS TOOL --

17:38.790 --> 17:41.088
IT IS CALLED THE CHOKE PEAR,

17:41.120 --> 17:45.454
ALTHOUGH I HAVE HEARD IT CALLED
THE PEAR OF ANGUISH.

17:47.600 --> 17:49.295
Tituba: [ CRIES ]

17:49.330 --> 17:54.063
Increase: IT IS INSERTED
INTO THE DARKER CAVITIES

17:54.100 --> 17:54.964
AND THEN...

17:55.000 --> 17:56.035
[ DEVICE CREAKING ]

17:56.070 --> 17:57.059
...OPENED UP,

17:57.110 --> 18:00.102
WITH THE EXPECTATION

18:00.140 --> 18:02.779
THAT THE SUBJECT, TOO,
WILL OPEN UP.

18:02.810 --> 18:06.348
NOW, TELL ME THE REAL NAMES.

18:09.780 --> 18:14.979
Cotton: MY FATHER, WHO ART
IN SALEM, HOLLOW BE THY NAME.

18:15.020 --> 18:17.580
THY KINGDOM'S DONE,

18:17.630 --> 18:20.497
YOUR WILL I SHUN,

18:20.530 --> 18:23.226
ON EARTH...

18:23.270 --> 18:26.194
AS IN THE HELL
YOU'D MAKE OF HEAVEN.

18:29.940 --> 18:31.931
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

18:34.310 --> 18:36.107
[ DEMONIC MOANING ]

18:43.450 --> 18:46.214
THE DEVIL HIMSELF
COME TO TAKE ME.

18:49.720 --> 18:51.585
TAKE ME, DEVIL.

18:51.630 --> 18:55.350
I SHOULD HAVE LIVED EVERY HOUR
ON EARTH AS IF IT WERE MY LAST.

18:55.400 --> 18:58.392
AND NOW IT IS.

19:03.410 --> 19:04.832
[ DEMONIC MOANING ]

19:04.870 --> 19:06.667
[ SHRIEKS ]

19:11.480 --> 19:13.141
[ YELLS ]

19:18.150 --> 19:20.311
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

19:51.020 --> 19:54.080
OUT OF DEATH COMES LIFE.

19:55.720 --> 19:58.985
I SEE NOW, LORD,
THAT IS YOUR TRUE FACE.

19:59.030 --> 20:01.555
[ GASPING ]

20:13.480 --> 20:16.074
[ LAUGHS ]

20:17.550 --> 20:19.871
OH!

20:19.910 --> 20:21.446
[ LAUGHS ]

20:23.720 --> 20:25.881
Titu ba:
[ BREATHING HEAVILY]

20:26.820 --> 20:31.086
YOU CANNOT KNOW WHAT I HAVE DONE

20:31.130 --> 20:34.019
OR WHO I HAVE SERVED

20:34.060 --> 20:36.699
UNTIL YOU KNOW WHY.

20:36.730 --> 20:38.163
Increase: SO...

20:41.000 --> 20:43.264
...THEN TELL ME.

20:43.310 --> 20:44.959
WHY?

20:45.010 --> 20:48.400
Tituba: FOR JUSTICE.

20:48.440 --> 20:50.078
I AM NOT A WITCH.

20:50.110 --> 20:52.874
I AM NOT A PURITAN.

20:52.910 --> 20:58.109
I AM OF THE ARAWAK TRIBE...

20:58.150 --> 21:00.653
OR I ONCE WAS.

21:00.690 --> 21:02.487
BUT I CLOSE MY EYES,

21:02.520 --> 21:06.229
AND I CAN STILL SEE THE GREEN
OF MY JUNGLE

21:06.260 --> 21:09.889
AND THE DEADLY WHITE
OF THE ENGLISHMEN'S FACES.

21:09.930 --> 21:12.319
I HAD NEVER SEEN SKIN LIKE THAT,

21:12.370 --> 21:16.397
SO WHITE WHEN WE SEE THEM
WALKING TOWARDS US,

21:16.440 --> 21:17.737
WE THINK THEY ARE GHOSTS.

21:17.770 --> 21:19.169
Increase: SLAVERS.

21:19.210 --> 21:21.929
Tituba: THEY SLAUGHTERED
MANY OF OUR MEN,

21:21.980 --> 21:25.245
CHAINED THE REST, AND HAVE
THEIR WAY WITH THE WOMEN.

21:25.280 --> 21:27.976
I AM TOO YOUNG
TO BE OF USE TO THEM,

21:28.020 --> 21:30.648
BUT MY MOTHER AND SISTERS
ARE NOT.

21:30.690 --> 21:32.681
AND THEY FORCED ME TO WATCH.

21:32.720 --> 21:36.178
LATER, IN CHAINS, I LOOK BACK,

21:36.220 --> 21:39.621
AND THEY'RE BURNING THE HUTS
OF MY VILLAGE,

21:39.660 --> 21:44.165
AND I SEE TWO RED EYES STARING
BACK AT ME, OUT OF THE TREES.

21:44.200 --> 21:46.418
AND THE RED EYES SPEAK TO ME,

21:46.470 --> 21:49.928
"TITUBA, YOU ARE MINE."

21:49.970 --> 21:54.737
Increase: SATAN SPEAKS TO EACH
OF US IN OUR OWN NATIVE TONGUE.

21:59.210 --> 22:03.340
AND NOW SHALL WE CONTINUE?

22:10.760 --> 22:14.719
Alden: SOMEONE CAME THROUGH
HERE QUITE RECENTLY...

22:14.760 --> 22:19.220
SOMEONE WHO DIDN'T KNOW
WHERE THEY WERE GOING...

22:19.270 --> 22:23.809
AND MOVED RADICALLY,
AS IF LOST OR...

22:23.840 --> 22:25.364
Cotton: [ URINATING ]

22:25.410 --> 22:28.573
[ LAUGHS ]

22:28.610 --> 22:30.373
Alden:
COTTON! WHAT IN THE HELL?

22:30.410 --> 22:32.173
Alden:
OH, NOT HELL, JOHNNY,

22:32.210 --> 22:33.541
NOR HEAVEN.

22:33.580 --> 22:35.138
JUST EARTH --

22:35.180 --> 22:37.683
GLORIOUS, GLORIOUS EARTH.

22:37.720 --> 22:39.585
Hale: I FEAR THE REVEREND
HAS GONE MAD.

22:39.620 --> 22:41.656
Alden: COTTON,
GET YOUR DRUNK ASS DOWN HERE.

22:41.690 --> 22:43.351
Cotton:
NO, SIR, I WILL NOT.

22:43.390 --> 22:45.426
I CAN SEE FAR MORE CLEARLY
FROM HERE.

22:45.460 --> 22:47.052
IN FACT, I CAN SEE EVERYTHING.

22:47.090 --> 22:49.422
GOD HIMSELF
WALKS AMONG THESE WOODS,

22:49.460 --> 22:53.760
TRAILING CLOUDS OF ANIMAL GLORY.

22:53.800 --> 22:54.892
Alden:
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

22:54.940 --> 22:57.090
Cotton:
I TOOK MY BOOTS OFF.

22:57.140 --> 22:58.368
Alden: YEAH, SO?

22:58.410 --> 23:01.106
Cotton:
SO, I FELT THE EARTH!

23:01.140 --> 23:06.840
I FELT THE RAW, SACRED EARTH
BENEATH MY NAKED FEET.

23:06.880 --> 23:10.179
I FELT THE EARTH BREATHE.

23:10.220 --> 23:11.209
Alden: GO HOME.

23:11.250 --> 23:13.081
IF YOUR GREAT INSIGHT IS REAL,

23:13.120 --> 23:15.680
IT WILL BE JUST AS REAL
IN YOUR CHAMBERS

23:15.720 --> 23:16.948
AND A WHOLE LOT SAFER.

23:16.990 --> 23:21.051
Cotton:
THE FOREST AIR AND THIS...

23:21.100 --> 23:25.025
STURDY TREE ARE MY TEACHERS NOW.

23:25.070 --> 23:26.867
Hale:
WE HAVEN'T TIME FOR THIS.

23:26.900 --> 23:28.868
Cotton:
I STILL HAVE MUCH TO LEARN!

23:28.900 --> 23:32.461
[ BELLOWS HISSING ]

23:32.510 --> 23:34.239
[ POKER SIZZLES ]

23:38.410 --> 23:42.972
Increase:
WHEN EXACTLY DID YOU SELL
YOUR SOUL TO THE DEVIL?

23:43.020 --> 23:47.309
Tituba: MY BODY WAS BOUGHT
AND SOLD MANY TIMES,

23:47.350 --> 23:49.113
BUT NEVER MY SOUL,

23:49.160 --> 23:51.424
NOT UNTIL I CAME TO SALEM.

23:51.460 --> 23:54.588
I AM A CHILD IN A CAGE,

23:54.630 --> 23:59.966
GIVEN LESS TO EAT
THAN THE ANIMALS ON THE SHIP.

24:00.000 --> 24:03.333
I FEAR I WILL NEVER
SEE THE SUN AGAIN.

24:03.370 --> 24:05.668
AND THEN A MAN COMES.

24:05.710 --> 24:07.735
IT WAS HE THAT BROUGHT ME
TO SALEM,

24:07.780 --> 24:09.634
ONLY TO BE BOUGHT
AND SOLD AGAIN.

24:09.680 --> 24:15.312
I AM SOLD FROM HAND TO HAND,
FROM MAN TO MAN.

24:15.350 --> 24:17.511
BUT AT LEAST I AM NO LONGER
IN A CAGE.

24:17.550 --> 24:20.018
AND MY FINAL OWNER IS NOT CRUEL.

24:20.050 --> 24:22.848
THE WOLCOTTS GIVE ME A BED
TO SLEEP IN.

24:22.890 --> 24:26.587
THEIR GIRL CHILD, MARY,
TREATS ME ALMOST LIKE A SISTER.

24:26.630 --> 24:32.865
BUT STILL AT NIGHT,
I WEEP FOR MY MOTHER,

24:32.900 --> 24:37.530
AND I RIDE A RIVER OF TEARS
OUT OF MY STRAW BED,

24:37.570 --> 24:40.971
INTO THE DARK WOODS.

24:41.010 --> 24:44.207
Increase: THE DARK WOODS?

24:44.250 --> 24:46.639
WHO DO YOU MEET
IN THE DARK WOODS?

24:49.750 --> 24:53.811
Tituba: THE KENAIMA.

24:53.860 --> 24:58.479
HE HAS COME TO SAVE ME --
SAVE ALL OF US.

24:58.530 --> 25:04.321
HE DRAWS TO HIM ALL WHO HURT,

25:04.370 --> 25:06.292
ALL WHO HIDE,

25:06.330 --> 25:08.036
ALL WHO HATE,

25:08.070 --> 25:10.630
ALL WHO THIRST FOR JUSTICE,

25:10.670 --> 25:16.802
GATHERS US INTO THE CIRCLE
AND PROMISES US A LEADER,

25:16.840 --> 25:18.398
A SAVIOR,

25:18.450 --> 25:22.409
ONE WHO WILL CRUSH OUR ENEMIES
WITH A MIGHTY FIST.

25:22.450 --> 25:24.145
AND HE KEEPS HIS PROMISE.

25:24.190 --> 25:31.028
Increase: GIRL,
I, TOO, KEEP MY PROMISES.

25:31.060 --> 25:33.756
AND I PROMISE YOU NOW

25:33.800 --> 25:39.864
I WILL PUT YOUR EYES OUT
THIS INSTANT

25:39.900 --> 25:44.064
IF YOU DO NOT TELL ME
WHO IS IN THE CIRCLE,

25:44.110 --> 25:46.601
WHO, THE NAMES,

25:46.640 --> 25:50.269
WHO IS IN THE CIRCLE OF WITCHES.

25:50.310 --> 25:52.676
TELL ME.

25:52.710 --> 25:54.473
[ GRUNTS ]

26:01.720 --> 26:03.415
WHAT FORTITU DE.

26:08.160 --> 26:12.859
SOLIDARITY AMONGST
THE RUDELY OPPRESSED.

26:12.900 --> 26:14.561
INSPIRING.

26:14.600 --> 26:18.707
IT'S -- IT'S ALL
SO VERY TOUCHING.

26:18.740 --> 26:21.903
BUT I TELL YOU, YOU'RE DUPED.

26:21.940 --> 26:24.204
THESE CREATURES
ARE NOT YOUR FRIENDS,

26:24.250 --> 26:26.548
NOR ANYONE'S FRIENDS.

26:26.580 --> 26:29.708
THEY ARE THE ENEMIES
OF ALL MANKIND.

26:29.750 --> 26:33.208
Tituba:
TELL ME, WHO STARTED THIS WAR

26:33.250 --> 26:35.810
BETWEEN WITCHES AND PURITANS,

26:35.860 --> 26:39.125
THE SCATTERED FEW OF THEM
OR THE MIGHTY MANY OF YOU?

26:39.160 --> 26:41.754
Increase:
BY YOUR OWN ADMISSION,

26:41.800 --> 26:45.099
THESE CREATURES HAVE SOLD
THEIR VERY SOULS

26:45.130 --> 26:47.166
FOR VENGEANCE TO THE DEVIL.

26:47.200 --> 26:48.497
IS THIS NOT SO?

26:48.540 --> 26:52.499
Tituba:
WERE YOUR PEOPLE NEVER SLAVES?

26:52.540 --> 26:56.078
DID THEY NEVER CRY OUT
IN THE WILDERNESS FOR JUSTICE?

26:56.110 --> 27:01.173
AND DID YOUR GOD NOT HEAR THEIR
CRIES AND ANSWER WITH THUNDER?

27:01.220 --> 27:04.917
DON'T YOU SEE?

27:04.950 --> 27:07.248
THERE ARE NO WITCHES,

27:07.290 --> 27:09.918
ONLY POOR PEOPLE LIKE ME,

27:09.960 --> 27:12.019
HUNTED AND HARRIED,

27:12.060 --> 27:13.755
TORTURED AND MURDERED,

27:13.800 --> 27:17.793
AND FOR NO REASON OTHER
THAN THEY ARE NOT YOU!

27:26.410 --> 27:31.541
Alden: SHE WAS HERE.
I'VE GOT HER TRACK AGAIN.

28:08.050 --> 28:10.211
NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS,

28:10.250 --> 28:13.048
JUST STAY CALM AND SAY NOTHING.

28:38.550 --> 28:40.677
Man: [ SNIFFING ]

28:40.710 --> 28:44.111
Alden: KAHYONHOWANEN
WENSI TEKENI EHNITA.

28:53.160 --> 28:57.096
RATKAHTHOS KENRAKEN YAKONKWE?

28:59.330 --> 29:01.264
Man: RAN KWE KARONYA.

29:01.300 --> 29:04.064
[ SPEAKS NATIVE LANGUAGE ]

29:13.510 --> 29:17.549
Hale: YOU ARE A MYSTERY
WITHIN A MYSTERY, CAPTAIN.

29:17.580 --> 29:19.889
WALK THE WOODS LIKE A PREDATOR,

29:19.920 --> 29:23.219
SPEAK TO SAVAGES
AS IF YOU WERE ONE OF THEM.

29:23.260 --> 29:26.423
Alden: THEY SAW HER,
BUT THEY DID NOT TOUCH HER.

29:26.460 --> 29:27.722
Hale:
AND YOU BELIEVE THEM?

29:27.760 --> 29:30.422
Alden: I DO.

29:30.460 --> 29:32.894
THEY USED A WORD
TO DESCRIBE HER.

29:32.930 --> 29:34.830
IT CAN MEAN A LOT
OF DIFFERENT THINGS,

29:34.870 --> 29:38.169
BUT IT USUALLY
JUST MEANS "CRAZY."

29:38.210 --> 29:41.008
Hale: MY DAUGHTER
IS MANY THINGS, CAPTAIN,

29:41.040 --> 29:44.248
BUT CRAZY IS NOT ONE OF THEM.

29:44.280 --> 29:48.114
Alden: WELL, LUCKY FOR HER
THEY THOUGHT SHE WAS.

29:48.150 --> 29:53.588
THEY THINK CRAZY PEOPLE
ARE WHAT WE CALL HOLY --

29:53.620 --> 29:56.180
WALKERS BETWEEN WORLDS.

29:56.220 --> 29:59.121
MAKE ANY SENSE TO YOU?

30:09.470 --> 30:12.200
[ CRICKETS CHIRPING ]

30:12.240 --> 30:15.505
Increase:
YOU ASK ME WHO BEGAN THIS WAR.

30:15.540 --> 30:19.101
AS ONE SCARRED

30:19.150 --> 30:23.109
WITH 40 YEARS SOLDIERING IN IT,

30:23.150 --> 30:25.289
I TELL YOU NOW...

30:25.320 --> 30:29.689
IT DOES NOT MATTER...

30:34.160 --> 30:36.526
...ONLY THAT IT END.

30:39.530 --> 30:42.169
AND END IT WILL.

30:44.940 --> 30:46.202
[ LIGHT CLATTER ]

30:46.240 --> 30:49.209
YOU AND YOUR KIND HAVE NO HOPE.

30:50.340 --> 30:55.414
YOU WILL BLEED,
AND YOU WILL HURT...

30:55.450 --> 30:58.317
AND YOU WILL DIE
IN A HOPELESS CAUSE.

30:58.350 --> 31:01.751
Tituba:
LOVE IS NOT A HOPELESS CAUSE.

31:01.790 --> 31:05.578
I WILL NOT BETRAY THE ONE
TRUE LOVE OF MY LIFE.

31:09.860 --> 31:12.397
Increase: I UNDERSTAND.

31:15.740 --> 31:19.608
FINALLY I UNDERSTAND IT ALL.

31:19.640 --> 31:21.505
I UNDERSTAND EVERYTHING.

31:21.540 --> 31:22.529
Titu ba: [ GASPS ]

31:22.580 --> 31:23.604
Increase: YOU POOR THING.

31:23.640 --> 31:26.177
JUST A LITTLE GIRL,

31:26.210 --> 31:30.840
KIDNAPPED, ENSLAVED, ALONE,

31:30.880 --> 31:35.180
SEEKING UNDERSTANDING,

31:35.220 --> 31:37.108
COMFORT...

31:37.160 --> 31:39.048
SEEKING LOVE.

31:39.090 --> 31:43.197
[ SIGHS ]

31:43.230 --> 31:46.358
DO YOU NOT SEE?

31:46.400 --> 31:49.096
I DO NOT DOUBT THAT YOU LOVE.

31:49.140 --> 31:53.463
BUT JUST FOR THIS ONE MOMENT
HERE ALONE WITH ME, BE HONEST,

31:53.510 --> 31:56.968
IF NOT WITH ME,
AT LEAST WITH YOURSELF.

31:57.010 --> 32:01.549
DO YOU REALLY BELIEVE
THAT THEY LOVE YOU

32:01.580 --> 32:04.879
AS MUCH AS YOU LOVE THEM?

32:04.920 --> 32:06.547
THINK, WOMAN.

32:06.590 --> 32:09.582
THINK OF THAT, THAT PERSON.

32:09.620 --> 32:11.827
PICTURE THEM IN YOUR MIND.

32:11.860 --> 32:13.782
YOU KNOW THEM SO WELL.

32:13.830 --> 32:15.559
CONSIDER WHO THEY ARE,

32:15.600 --> 32:19.593
NOT WHO YOU WISH THEM TO BE,
BUT WHO THEY REALLY ARE,

32:19.630 --> 32:22.292
AND ASK YOURSELF,
WERE THEY HERE,

32:22.340 --> 32:25.935
WOULD THEY OR WOULD THEY NOT
OFFER UP YOUR NAME

32:25.970 --> 32:27.506
TO SAVE THEMSELVES?

32:32.480 --> 32:35.472
AND THIS IS THE PERSON
THAT YOU LOVE

32:35.520 --> 32:39.616
AND WHO WILL NEVER
LOVE YOU THE SAME WAY.

32:39.650 --> 32:45.486
IS IT WORTH IT ALL,
THE HORRORS YOU HAVE ENDURED,

32:45.530 --> 32:47.054
AND THE AGONIES...

32:53.130 --> 32:57.635
...AND THE UGLY, UGLY DEATH
YOU HAVE IN FRONT OF YOU?

32:57.670 --> 33:01.128
IS THAT REALLY WHAT YOU WANT,

33:01.180 --> 33:05.378
NOW THAT YOU HAVE NOW ADMITTED
TO YOURSELF

33:05.410 --> 33:08.971
WHO THEY REALLY ARE?

33:09.020 --> 33:10.874
TITUBA...

33:10.920 --> 33:16.449
DO YOU KNOW THE GREATEST
PLEASURE IN THE WORLD?

33:16.490 --> 33:21.325
IT IS WHEN THE PAIN STOPS.

33:21.360 --> 33:22.622
Tituba: [ CRIES ]

33:22.660 --> 33:24.560
Increase:
AND STOP IT WILL.

33:24.600 --> 33:28.491
YOU HAVE BUT TO TELL ME A NAME.

33:28.540 --> 33:30.337
JUST WHISPER IT.

33:30.370 --> 33:32.065
Tituba: [ SOBBING ]

33:32.110 --> 33:35.830
Increase:
TELL ME WHO IS THE LEADER

33:35.880 --> 33:40.044
OF THE WITCHES IN SALEM.

33:40.080 --> 33:43.811
Tituba:
ON MY SOUL, THE ONE YOU SEEK...

33:43.850 --> 33:45.841
[ WHISPERS INDISTINCTLY ]

33:48.520 --> 33:50.579
[ CRYING ]

33:59.870 --> 34:02.430
Anne: [ GASPING ]

34:12.080 --> 34:13.707
[ SIGHS ]

34:19.650 --> 34:22.050
[ ANIMALS CHATTERING ]

34:28.160 --> 34:29.457
[ SOBBING ]

34:32.230 --> 34:34.369
[ GASPS ]

34:34.400 --> 34:37.665
[ RAINING ]

34:43.580 --> 34:46.879
IT COULD BE WORSE.

34:46.910 --> 34:49.276
IT COULD BE RAINING.

34:51.850 --> 34:53.841
[ LAUGHING ]

34:55.420 --> 34:56.455
[ RAIN STOPS ]

34:56.490 --> 34:57.457
[ GASPS ]

34:57.490 --> 34:59.287
[ BIRD CAWING ]

34:59.330 --> 35:00.149
[ TWIG SNAPS ]

35:00.190 --> 35:01.122
[ GASPS ]

35:01.160 --> 35:02.889
[ BIRD SHRIEKS, WINGS FLAP ]

35:02.930 --> 35:05.990
[ DEMONIC MOANING ]

35:06.030 --> 35:08.362
[ GASPS ]

35:11.040 --> 35:15.773
Demon: AT LAST,
YOU FOUND YOUR WAY HOME.

35:20.780 --> 35:22.418
[ LAUGHS EVILLY ]

35:22.450 --> 35:24.589
Anne: [ SCREAMS ]

35:24.620 --> 35:27.214
Demon: [ GROWLING ]

35:31.460 --> 35:32.529
Anne: [ SCREAMS ]

35:32.560 --> 35:34.289
Alden: ANNE!

35:34.330 --> 35:36.457
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

35:36.500 --> 35:38.365
Anne: [ GASPS LIGHTLY ]

35:38.400 --> 35:40.789
[ SOBBING ]

35:40.830 --> 35:43.936
[ GASPS ]

35:43.970 --> 35:46.109
Hale: OH! OH.

35:46.140 --> 35:48.438
I THOUGHT I'D LOST YOU.

35:48.480 --> 35:50.869
Anne: ME TOO.

35:50.910 --> 35:54.539
HOW?

35:54.580 --> 35:57.219
HOW?

35:59.820 --> 36:02.516
HOW DID YOU FIND ME?

36:04.020 --> 36:05.681
Hale: [ SIGHS ]

36:05.730 --> 36:07.322
GIVE ALL CREDIT TO CAPTAIN ALDEN

36:07.360 --> 36:11.296
AND HIS PRETERNATURAL SKILLS
IN THESE WOODS.

36:11.330 --> 36:15.130
Alden:
FOLLOWING THE TRACKS WAS EASY
ONCE I FOUND MY WAY OUT HERE.

36:15.170 --> 36:17.832
BUT WHAT I CAN'T FIGURE IS HOW
YOU GOT SO FAR OUT OF SALEM

36:17.870 --> 36:22.739
LEAVING SO FEW TRACKS AND TRACES
BETWEEN HERE AND THERE.

36:36.790 --> 36:40.920
Anne: I AM A SILLY THING,
AND IN A FIT OF PETULANCE,

36:40.960 --> 36:44.054
I-I RAN INTO THESE WOODS

36:44.100 --> 36:48.161
WITHOUT THINKING WHERE I WAS
GOING OR HOW LATE IT WAS...

36:48.200 --> 36:50.168
UNTIL IT WAS TOO LATE.

36:50.200 --> 36:54.603
Alden: WITHOUT LEAVING
ANY TRACKS OUT OF SALEM.

36:54.640 --> 36:59.077
Anne: IT -- IT RAINED BRIEFLY
WHILE I WAS...

36:59.110 --> 37:02.113
WANDERING.

37:02.150 --> 37:04.516
PERHAPS THAT WASH ED AWAY
MY TRACKS,

37:04.550 --> 37:07.610
OR PERHAPS YOU JUST
DIDN'T FIND THEM.

37:07.650 --> 37:10.312
IN EITHER CASE...

37:13.730 --> 37:15.129
PLEASE FORGIVE ME

37:15.160 --> 37:18.197
FOR THE TROUBLE
I'VE PUT YOU BOTH THROUGH.

37:18.230 --> 37:22.337
Hale: THANK YOU.

37:24.770 --> 37:27.534
Alden: WELL, I'M SURE YOU'D DO
THE SAME THING FOR ME

37:27.570 --> 37:29.299
IF I EVER NEEDED...

37:29.340 --> 37:31.479
RESCUING.

37:42.190 --> 37:44.556
[ DOG BARKING ]

37:44.590 --> 37:46.251
Mary: [ SOBBING ]

37:46.290 --> 37:48.349
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

37:55.600 --> 37:58.330
Increase:
YOU WERE CORRECT.

37:58.370 --> 38:00.008
SHE'S A REMARKABLE YOUNG WOMAN.

38:00.040 --> 38:01.735
Mary: HMM.

38:01.780 --> 38:05.443
Increase: I CAN UNDERSTAND
WHY SHE'S NOT MERELY YOUR --

38:05.480 --> 38:08.176
YOUR SERVANT,
BUT YOUR FRIEND, AS WELL.

38:08.210 --> 38:10.849
I'VE DISCOVERED SOMETHING
QUITE EXTRAORDINARY.

38:10.880 --> 38:13.747
I FIND SO MUCH LOVE.

38:13.790 --> 38:15.257
Mary: LOVE?

38:15.290 --> 38:16.609
Increase:
WHAT I DID NOT UNDERSTAND

38:16.660 --> 38:18.013
WAS THAT THE CHIEF WITCH
OF SALEM

38:18.060 --> 38:21.029
IS NOT MERELY HER LEADER...

38:21.060 --> 38:22.698
BUT HER LOVER.

38:22.730 --> 38:24.368
Mary: SHE CONFESSED?

38:24.400 --> 38:28.291
Increase: LOVE IS A-A TWO-FACED
COIN, IS IT NOT?

38:28.340 --> 38:30.865
AND ONE FACE IS SURELY BETRAYAL.

38:34.140 --> 38:35.869
DO YOU MIND?

38:35.910 --> 38:37.537
Mary: WHAT?

38:37.580 --> 38:39.548
OH. YES, PLEASE.

38:39.580 --> 38:41.309
Increase:
I RARELY INDULGE,

38:41.350 --> 38:46.413
BUT...I FEEL THE NEED
OF A RESTORATIVE.

38:52.390 --> 38:55.154
OH, GEORGE [CHUCKLES] GEORGE.

38:55.200 --> 38:58.055
HE'S ALWAYS CULTIVATED THE
FINEST CELLAR IN THE COLONY,

38:58.100 --> 38:59.624
HUH?

38:59.670 --> 39:00.967
WHAT WAS I SAYING?

39:01.000 --> 39:03.195
Mary: LOVE.

39:03.240 --> 39:05.834
Increase: YES.

39:05.870 --> 39:09.033
YOU KNOW...

39:09.080 --> 39:14.302
IT IS TRUE THAT, AND NO ONE WILL
ADMIT, THAT LOVE IS NEVER EQUAL.

39:14.350 --> 39:19.083
AND IN ITS INEQUALITY
LIES ITS FRAGILITY,

39:19.120 --> 39:22.351
FOR THE ONE WHO IS LOVED LESS

39:22.390 --> 39:26.429
WILL ONE DAY FIND
LOVE TASTES LIKE ASHES.

39:26.460 --> 39:29.827
THAT IS INDEED
WHAT POOR MISS TITUBA FOUND.

39:29.860 --> 39:33.591
BUT SHE DID TELL ME EVERYTHING,

39:33.630 --> 39:37.168
AND SHE STARTED
WITH MERCY LEWIS.

39:37.200 --> 39:39.202
Mary: MERCY?

39:39.240 --> 39:42.607
Increase: MERCY LEWIS
MAY WELL HAVE BEGUN

39:42.640 --> 39:45.575
AS A VICTIM OF MALICE,
BUT SHE --

39:45.610 --> 39:50.047
SHE WAS MADE WITCH BY THE VERY
BEAST THAT ASSAILED HER.

39:50.080 --> 39:51.616
Mary: SHE'S NOT HERE.

39:54.050 --> 39:55.358
SHE'S NOT RETURNED.

39:55.390 --> 39:58.450
Increase: WELL,
IT IS NO GREAT MATTER.

39:58.490 --> 40:01.084
Al-TER ALL, WHERE CAN SHE RUN TO?

40:01.130 --> 40:04.588
I WILL HAVE HER AND HER GIRLS

40:04.630 --> 40:07.497
BY THE TIME THE SUN COMES UP.

40:14.410 --> 40:16.037
AHH.

40:16.080 --> 40:19.470
[ SETS GLASS DOWN ]

40:19.510 --> 40:25.312
WHEN I FIRST RETURNED TO SALEM,

40:25.350 --> 40:29.150
I WAS CONVINCED
THAT SATAN'S TRUE PARTNER

40:29.190 --> 40:30.987
WAS RIGHT IN FRONT OF ME

40:31.020 --> 40:34.899
AND ALL I NEED DO IS REACH OUT
MY HAND TO TAKE HER.

40:34.930 --> 40:37.490
YOU CAN IMAGINE MY SHOCK
TO DISCOVER

40:37.530 --> 40:39.896
THAT CAPTAIN JOHN ALDEN

40:39.930 --> 40:43.798
STANDS BEHIND ALL
OF SALEM'S HORROR.

40:45.440 --> 40:49.672
[ SIGHING ]

40:49.710 --> 40:53.999
I FEAR I...NEED A BREATH OF AIR.

40:54.050 --> 40:57.247
WILL YOU WALK WITH ME,
MARY SIBLEY,

40:57.280 --> 41:01.011
IN THE EVENING AIR...

41:01.050 --> 41:06.522
WHERE WE MAY HAVE
A GOOD VANTAGE POINT

41:06.560 --> 41:09.449
FROM WHICH TO WITNESS
AN ARREST?

41:13.530 --> 41:17.136
Alden: I'M TEMPTED TO GO BACK,
SEE IF COTTON'S ALL RIGHT.

41:17.170 --> 41:19.206
HE COULD GET LOST IN THOSE WOODS

41:19.240 --> 41:21.879
AND WAKE UP INSIDE THE BELLY
OF A BEAR.

41:21.910 --> 41:24.799
Man: THERE HE IS!

41:39.560 --> 41:41.323
Selectman: JOHN ALDEN...

41:44.570 --> 41:47.892
...BY ORDER OF INCREASE MATHER

41:47.930 --> 41:49.989
AND IN THE NAME
OF THE SELECTMEN OF SALEM,

41:50.040 --> 41:52.361
I PLACE YOU UNDER ARREST.

42:01.110 --> 42:04.409
Alden:
WHAT FOR THIS TIME?

42:04.450 --> 42:06.247
SWEARING IN PUBLIC?

42:06.290 --> 42:08.508
Selectman: WITCHCRAI-T.

42:08.560 --> 42:10.551
[ CROWD MURMURING ]

42:10.590 --> 42:13.525
Man:
DISARM HIM, SHACKLE HIM.

42:13.560 --> 42:15.050
Anne: NO!

42:15.100 --> 42:17.489
NO! FATHER, STOP THEM!

42:17.530 --> 42:19.589
FATHER, PLEASE!

42:19.630 --> 42:20.892
PLEASE! YOU HAVE THE POWER
TO DO SOMETHING!

42:20.930 --> 42:24.229
Hale: WAIT. Shh!

42:40.920 --> 42:43.582
[ HORSES WHINNY ]

42:46.130 --> 42:49.190
[ BELL TOLLING ]

42:49.230 --> 42:52.791
[ DOG BARKING ]
